release_note: Added support for certain content displays Fixed an issue affecting DRM playback over AirPlay Feature enhancements and bug fixes

Optimized for iOS 14 support Download manager optimizations Chromecast iOS 14 usability improvements Please ensure you have enabled Local Network permissions in your system settings if you do not see your Chromecast device on the network
Improvements to analytics Fixed an issue affecting background audio for some users Fixed an issue affecting closed caption for some users Feature enhancements and bug fixes
Optimizations for content loading Improvements to error messaging Fixes for Chromecast streaming for certain users Bug fixes and stability improvements
Addresses an issue that was affecting downloads for offline on iOS 11 and 12 Fixes some intermittent issues with subtitles Fixes deep linking to specific videos Performance improvements
Accessibility improvements to voice control Stability improvements and bug fixes
Support for Spanish German French and Portuguese user interfaces Improvements to continuous playback Improved metadata on videos Increased character support while searching Stability improvements
Improvements to Extras Improvements to My List UX enhancements to video player Stability improvements and bug fixes

Enhanced subtitle support Subtitle preference setting now persists across all videos Enhanced support request functionality Fixed a bug with Extras not displaying properly Fixed a bug that left locks on screen on some videos after signing up
UX enhancements and stability improvements Improved contact form Optimizations for offline downloaded videos
